Thanks for downloading the Vigilance Theme for MangoBlog. 
This is an adaptation of the theme produced by Jethro for Wordpress, see the original here: http://themes.jestro.com/vigilance/

Install Instructions:
1. Unzip to {mangoblog_install_dir}/skins/
2. Edit sidebar.cfm lines 17 & 18 updating to your twitter account and email subscription location.
3. In your MangoBlog admin go to the themes section and select the Vigilance Theme.

Feel free to send me any questions or comments.

